-- ============================================================
-- JUVEDERM VOLUMA XC
-- product_id: 6c8f72f0-887f-484a-a588-0bb9bd8052c9
-- FDA-cleared: cheek augmentation (2013), chin augmentation (2021)
-- Technology: Vycross (cross-linked HA), G' prime ~800 Pa, 24 mg/mL HA
